{"tid":328751,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（真·勇武）港社工過羅湖關後宣讀《零八憲章》被帶走","createTime":"2017-07-19T22:58:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-20T02:39:22.000Z","uid":41351,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"af50926b5e359d8be7c9985b62072bbdf2b57ff8","tid":328751,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T22:58:17.000Z","msg":"基督徒社工呂智恆 羅湖橋宣讀《零八憲章》被帶走下落未明<br />\n基督徒社工呂智恆，昨晚7時左右在羅湖過關之後，在羅湖橋宣讀劉曉波著作《我沒有敵人》和《零八憲章》，據知15分後即被帶走，暫時未知身在何方。<br />\n<br />\n他在出發前曾經表示，希望在劉曉波頭七的這一天，把劉的民主精神帶回家，行動同時會為香港4位被DQ的立法會議員、中港的民主和人權禱告。他希望香港人不要以冷漠為榮、無知為樂，「今日中共可逼害劉曉波等人，同樣可以加害香港人，特別係23條立法在即，希望香港人再次有勇氣抵抗壓迫！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/20/065538_7b35b05d039e99d54abb32f5eaf8dd85.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F20%2F065538_7b35b05d039e99d54abb32f5eaf8dd85.jpg&h=044ab95d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56977912&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170720\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56977912%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170720&d=9VWZnW%2BNYN987grUXULf9v7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=1ae5c555\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56977912%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170720&h=e3698393\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56977912&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170720</a><br />\n支那人都唔理 港義士走去理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上次有人舉牌聲援佔領 都坐四年<br />\n今次仲唔坐返六七年"},{"pid":"065ab1b2174e75fd24e0d565e08786c4bd602733","tid":328751,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T23:02:59.000Z","msg":"突發"},{"pid":"db937da29f7407f00ac548f9bf3e1447aecc08e8","tid":328751